

🧠 PHASE 1 – Python + ML Foundations

1️⃣ Python (Must)

✅ Best Course:

“Complete Python Bootcamp” – by Jose Portilla

Why?

Practical

Beginner → Intermediate

Covers OOP (important for FastAPI & AI services)


You don’t need:

50-hour mega deep theory course



---

2️⃣ Machine Learning (Practical)

✅ Best Course:

“Machine Learning A-Z” – Kirill Eremenko

Why?

Beginner friendly

Practical projects

Covers regression, classification, clustering

Enough math (not excessive)


⚠ Don’t get stuck in heavy math courses.


---

🧠 PHASE 2 – Deep Learning

3️⃣ PyTorch

✅ Best Course:

“PyTorch for Deep Learning” – Daniel Bourke

Why?

Modern

Practical

Clear explanations

Not overly academic


OR

TensorFlow Option

“Deep Learning with TensorFlow 2.0” – Jose Portilla

Choose ONE (PyTorch preferred).


